      "description": "The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} has these weaknesses:\n\nForbiddance. The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can't enter a residence without an invitation from an occupant.\n\nRunning Water. The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} takes 20 Acid damage if it ends its turn in running water.\n\nStake to the Heart. The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} is destroyed if a weapon that deals Piercing damage is driven into the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}'s heart while the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} has the Incapacitated condition.\n\nSunlight. The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} takes 20 Radiant damage if it starts its turn in sunlight. While in sunlight, it has Disadvantage on attack rolls and ability checks.",
